SummaryExplanation.val:
In FY2019 - FY2023 Evolved SBIRS Ground (Project 657106) and Space Modernization Initiative (Project 657009) funds transferred from PE 1206441F to PE 1206442F in order to isolate the SBIRS PoR development through completion, align SMI with future efforts, and merge Next-Gen OPIR Space and Ground funds in the same PE. A new Project 657120 (Evolved SBIRS Space) was created within PE 1206442F for transparency between Space and Ground efforts.

FY2019: 
SMI: +$136.201M transferred from PE 1206441F, +$52.000M added for Demonstrations, and -$1.645M for inflation adjustment; 
Next-Gen OPIR-Space: +$67.192M transferred from PE 1206441F, +$131.513M added for development;
Next-Gen OPIR-Ground: +$28.847M transferred from PE 1206441F, +$158.000M added for risk reduction activities and implementation of cyber modernization
